    <summary>QT frontend to hotot: a lightweight &amp; open source micro blogging client</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            Hotot, is a lightweight &amp; open source micro blogging client with a
            minimalistic yet stylish interface. Available for Gtk and QT, it is quite 
            feature rich:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Extensions support</li>
            <li>Preview images and videos</li>
            <li>Image service integration</li>
            <li>Theme support</li>
            <li>Threaded conversations</li>
            <li>View geo-information</li>
            <li>Kismet firewall</li>
            <li>Notification system</li>
            <li>Multi-column view</li>
            <li>Real-time updates</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            This is the QT frontend.
        </p>

    </description>
